<template>
  <v-checkbox v-model="isChecked" label="Check me"></v-checkbox>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  computed: {
    isChecked: {
      get() {
        return this.$store.state.isChecked;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.$store.commit('setChecked', value);
      },
    },
  },
};
</script>
